OL,5,G1700 Secret Nazi Bases
OL,6,     FHitler's Secret Underground City:
OL,7,     FIn Poland lies a forgotten Nazi
OL,8,     Fcomplex which could have sheltered
OL,9,     Fup to 27,244 people from Allied
OL,10,     Fbombs, the purpose of which
OL,11,     Flargely remains a mystery.
